    <div class="accordion-item">
      <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingOne">
        <button class="accordion-button" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseOne" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="collapseOne" style="background-color:#524FF7; border-radius:10px;">
          <i class="fa-solid fa-suitcase"></i>
          <span style="margin-left:10px;">Solo Travelers</span>
        </button>
      </h2>
    <div id="collapseOne" class="accordion-collapse collapse show" aria-labelledby="headingOne" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Don’t walk alone after dark.</li>
          <li>Don’t take pictures without asking for permission – or expect to pay for the privilege if you do.</li>
          <li>Carry a driving license and a little money in your pocket for the traffic police’s ‘lunch’.</li>
          <li>Don’t pay for anything upfront without seeing the room/item/goods first.</li>
          <li>Be vigilant when in public places.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingTwo">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseTwo" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseTwo" style="background-color:#7774FF; border-radius:10px;">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-map-pin"></i>
        <span style="margin-left:10px;">Unknown Streets</span>
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="collapseTwo" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingTwo" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Exploring unknown streets can be an exciting adventure, but it's important to prioritize your safety.</li>
          <li>When navigating unfamiliar areas, consider the following safety precautions:
          Stay alert and be aware of your surroundings at all times. Pay attention to the people around you and any potential risks or hazards.</li>
          <li>Stay alert and be aware of your surroundings at all times. Pay attention to the people around you and any potential risks or hazards.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingThree">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseThree" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseThree" style="background-color:#AAA8FF; border-radius:5px;">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-house"></i>
        <span style="margin-left:10px;">Where to Stay</span>
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="collapseThree" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingThree" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
      <div class="accordion-body">
      <ul>
        <li>When it comes to choosing accommodation, safety is paramount, especially for women travelers.</li>
        <li>Prioritize well-established accommodations: Opt for reputable hotels, guesthouses, or hostels that have positive reviews and a track record of providing safe environments for their guests.</li>
        <li>Research and choose accommodations that prioritize security measures and have a good reputation for hosting women travelers.</li>
        <li>Location matters: Select accommodations in safe and well-populated areas, preferably near main streets or public transportation.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
  </div>
  <div class="accordion-item">
    <h2 class="accordion-header" id="headingFour">
      <button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapseFour" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapseFour" style="background-color:#D2D1FF; border-radius:5px;">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-venus"></i>
        <span style="margin-left:10px;">Women in the World</span>
      </button>
    </h2>
    <div id="collapseFour" class="accordion-collapse collapse" aria-labelledby="headingFour" data-bs-parent="#accordionExample">
      <div class="accordion-body">
        <ul>
          <li>Women traveling alone or in groups can have incredible and enriching experiences.</li>
          <li>To ensure a safe journey, it's important to prioritize personal safety.</li>
          <li>Some key tips include: Research your destination: Familiarize yourself with the local culture, customs, and laws.</li>
          <li>Learn about any potential safety concerns or specific precautions to take for women travelers.</li>
          <li>Plan and share your itinerary: Create a detailed itinerary and share it with a trusted friend or family member.</li>
          <li>Keep them updated on your whereabouts and check in regularly.</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>


</div>
  <div class="tab-pane fade" id="review-tab-pane" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="review-tab" tabindex="0">
    <div class="d-flex align-items-start flex-wrap">
      <% @city.itineraries.each do |itinerary| %>
        <% if itinerary.review.present? %>
          <div class="col-12 p-4 mb-2 mt-2 border" style="border-radius:5px;  box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);">
            <h4 style="color: #524FF7;;"><%= itinerary.user.first_name %> <%= itinerary.user.last_name %></h4>
            <%= itinerary.review %>
          </div>
        <% end %>
      <% end %>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
